        <h1>Deep Link Quick Test</h1>
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="/pin_shoppingbag.png" alt="Pinterest plus shopping bag icon">
        </div>
        <h2>
          This is a quick test site of Pinterest shopping in-app browser deep-link closing protocol.
        </h2>
        <div class="bttns">
          <a href="pinterest://checkoutPaymentNotify?event=close&source=walmart" class="bttn primary">Close Pinterest Shopping Browser</a>
        </div>
      </div>
			<div class="resource-list">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="https://business.pinterest.com/sk/blog/new-tools-for-shopify-merchants-on-pinterest/">Pinterest: Introducing Hosted Checkout</a>
